    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and a few small door dings, and the interior upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining on the carpets. While it runs and drives consistently, it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads or a suspension tune-up. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
