    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with all systems functioning perfectly and a complete, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that needs nothing but a new home.",
