    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my trips around town. Whether you're looking for a dependable commuter or something for weekend adventures, this car is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera features the high-revving 3.4L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and rear-engine weight bias provide the quintessential 911 experience. Recent service includes a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a rear main seal replacement, addressing key longevity concerns. Finished in Arctic Silver over black leather, this driver-focused example balances mechanical purity with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Runs well. Title in hand.",
