    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV offers the perfect balance of performance and daily practicality. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use and garage storage. Inside, the premium leather upholstery has been conditioned regularly and shows minimal wear, while the cabin remains smoke-free and pristine. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health, benefiting from a complete service history and a recent comprehensive inspection. With plenty of life left on the tires and a freshly detailed interior, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with complete confidence.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
